episodes.description: E3 was this week and yall were dying to know what we thought. Honestly the show was lack luster and we didn't hesitate to tell you why. If you get butt hurt easily this show isn't what you want to listen to.

Mortal Kombat X, Battlefield Hardline, Homefront Revolution and the Oculus Rift coming to Chuck E Cheese? What?!?! Sit back and enjoy the pre E3 show.

episodes.title: Episode 20 | Tick Is Negrodamus?
episodes.description: This is one of the few times Tick has ever been correct about something. I'm sure a hundred episodes down the rode & beyond he'll still be reminding us. Enjoy!
